{"tid":1908994,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"睇歷史法國廣陵王多數都廢，有個仲要玩針。。。。。。","createTime":"2020-03-03T15:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T10:44:32.000Z","uid":7439,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"06d4c22cde5d9a3d15955a62bc8a9c8662706128","tid":1908994,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:57:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>西漢 劉胥（前2世紀？－前54年）</ins></strong><br />\n漢武帝第四子<br />\n<br />\n無腦<br />\n<blockquote>胥壯大，好倡樂逸游，力扛鼎，空手搏熊彘猛獸。動作無法度，故終不得為漢嗣。</blockquote><br />\n玩詛咒<br />\n<blockquote>始，昭帝時，胥見上年少無子，有覬欲心。而楚地巫鬼，胥迎女巫李女須，使下神祝詛。<br />\n宣帝即位，胥曰：「太子孫何以反得立？」復令女須祝詛如前。</blockquote><br />\n想造反又唔敢，笠水自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>即以綬自絞死。及八子郭昭君等二人皆自殺。天子加恩，赦王諸子皆為庶人，賜謚曰厲王。立六十四年而誅，國除。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>東漢 劉荊（1世紀－67年）</ins></strong><br />\n光武帝第八子<br />\n<br />\n玩偽造文書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>荊性刻急隱害。<br />\n光武崩，大行在前殿，荊哭不哀，而作飛書，封以方底，令蒼頭詐稱東海王彊舅大鴻臚郭況書與彊曰<br />\n強得書惶怖，即執其使，封書上之。</blockquote><br />\nff系列 -想起兵<br />\n<blockquote>時西羌反，荊不得志，冀天下因羌驚動有變，私迎能為星者與謀議。帝聞之，乃徙封荊廣陵王，遣之國。其後荊復呼相工謂曰：<span style=\"color: red;\">「我貌類先帝。先帝三十得天下，我今亦三十，可起兵未？」</span>相者詣吏告之，荊惶恐，自繫獄。帝復加恩，不考極其事，下詔不得臣屬吏人，唯食租如故，使相、中尉謹宿衛之。</blockquote><br />\n又．想造反又唔敢，笠水自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>荊猶不改。其後使巫祭祀祝詛，有司舉奏，請誅之，荊自殺。立二十九年死。帝憐傷之，賜謚曰思王。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>西晉 司馬遹（278年－300年4月27日）</ins></strong><br />\n晉惠帝司馬衷唯一的兒子，晉惠帝即位後冊立其為皇太子。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>時望氣者言廣陵有天子氣，故封為廣陵王，邑五萬戶。惠帝即位，立為皇太子。</blockquote><br />\n古代金錢師<br />\n<blockquote>及長，不好學，惟與左右嬉戲，不能尊敬保傅。<br />\n愛埤車小馬，令左右馳騎，斷其鞅勒，使墮地為樂。或有犯忤者，手自捶擊之。性拘小忌，不許繕壁修牆，正瓦動屋。而于宮中為市，使人屠酤，手揣斤兩，輕重不差。其母本屠家女也，故太子好之。<span style=\"color: red;\">又令西園賣葵菜、藍子、雞、面之屬，而收其利。</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">玩針</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>舍人杜錫以太子非賈后所生，而後性凶暴，深以為憂，每盡忠規勸太子修德進善，遠於讒謗。太子怒，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">使人以針著錫常所坐氈中而剌之。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n想笠水？冇咁易<br />\n<blockquote>初，太子恐見鴆，恆自煮食於前。慮以告劉振，振乃徙太子于小坊中，絕不與食，宮中猶於牆壁上過食與太子。慮乃逼太子以藥，太子不肯服，因如廁，慮以藥杵椎殺之，太子大呼，聲聞於外。時年二十三。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>北魏 元羽 （470年－501年6月19日）</ins></strong><br />\n魏獻文帝拓跋弘第四子<br />\n<br />\n死law撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>典決京師獄訟<br />\n還領廷尉卿</blockquote><br />\n想南伐 有冇清john?<br />\n<blockquote>車駕南伐，羽進號衞將軍，除使持節、都督青齊光南青四州諸軍事、征東大將軍、開府、青州刺史。</blockquote><br />\n南齊督豫州、輔國將軍、豫州刺史 裴叔業：日操夜操想搵我做沙包 你都戇撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>偽徐州刺史廣陵王率二萬人，騎五千匹，至龍亢，璝等拒戰不敵。叔業三萬餘人助之，數道攻虜。虜新至，營未立，於是大敗。<span style=\"color: red;\">廣陵王與數十騎走，官軍追獲其節。</span>虜又遣偽將劉藻、高匆繼至，叔業率軍迎擊破之，<span style=\"color: red;\">再戰，斬首萬級，獲生口三千人，器仗驢馬絹布千萬計。</span></blockquote><br />\n沉船勾二嫂，死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>羽先淫員外郎馮俊興妻，夜因私遊，為俊興所擊。積日祕匿，薨於府，年三十二。<br />\n贈使持節、侍中、驃騎大將軍、司徒公、冀州刺史，給羽葆鼓吹、班劍四十人，諡曰惠。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>北魏 元恭(魏節閔帝)（498年－532年6月21日；在位531年-532年） </ins></strong><br />\n上面個仔<br />\n<blockquote>前廢帝，諱恭，字脩業，廣陵惠王羽之子也，母曰王氏。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>正始中，襲爵。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n稱帝就稱帝，乜X泰呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>太尉公尒朱度律奉進璽綬袞冕之服，乃就輅車，百官侍衞，入自建春、雲龍門，昇太極前殿，羣臣拜賀。<br />\n詔曰：「可大赦天下，以魏為大魏，改建明二年為<span style=\"color: red;\">普泰</span>元年。」</blockquote><br />\n信佛有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n<blockquote>夏四月辛巳，齊獻武王與廢帝至邙山，使魏蘭根慰諭洛邑，且觀帝之為人。蘭根忌帝雅德，還致毀謗，竟從崔㥄議，廢帝於崇訓佛寺，而立平陽王脩為帝。帝既失位，乃賦詩曰：「朱門久可患，紫極非情玩。顛覆立可待，一年三易換。時運正如此，唯有修真觀。」<br />\n太昌初，帝殂於門下外省，時年三十五。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5143f69958dd62bc2f9d5be5c66599feba34b832","tid":1908994,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>錫字世嘏。少有盛名，起家長沙王乂文學，累遷太子中舍人。性亮直忠烈，屢諫湣懷太子，言辭懇切，太子患之。<span style=\"color: red;\">後置針著錫常所坐處氈中，刺之流血。</span>他日，太子問錫：「向著何事？」錫對：「醉不知。」太子詰之曰：「君喜責人，何自作過也。」</blockquote>"},{"pid":"94b26b5d5df56a4ae8aa55ea42c567f98d299f82","tid":1908994,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5143f69958dd62bc2f9d5be5c66599feba34b832","tid":1908994,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>錫字世嘏。少有盛名，起家長沙王乂文學，累遷太子中舍人。性亮直忠烈，屢諫湣懷太子，言辭懇切，太子患之。<span style=\"color: red;\">後置針著錫常所坐處氈中，刺之流血。</span>他日，太子問錫：「向著何事？」錫對：「醉不知。」太子詰之曰：「君喜責人，何自作過也。」</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:08:13.000Z","msg":"滅吳統一三國嘅大功臣杜預之子竟然遭受咁嘅待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n針完人仲要鬧人抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b41c3467ee919e9d488ef36bf1b537451e79a1d","tid":1908994,"uid":117275,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:25:54.000Z","msg":"1.5倍w , 跑出黎p 都無 講經咩"},{"pid":"4a60372548f300b098b98152786744377114f203","tid":1908994,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b41c3467ee919e9d488ef36bf1b537451e79a1d","tid":1908994,"uid":117275,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:25:54.000Z","msg":"1.5倍w , 跑出黎p 都無 講經咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa8ae0396d95e637e0ecbd011797d22027af9dd","tid":1908994,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b70e00346e6a126434947cc80979bbe65f45dc","tid":1908994,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T21:20:13.000Z","msg":"N賓前世做皇帝"},{"pid":"e15b808f15559d743d36c927ba60e69d68fc8c2b","tid":1908994,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34b70e00346e6a126434947cc80979bbe65f45dc","tid":1908994,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T21:20:13.000Z","msg":"N賓前世做皇帝"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T21:23:35.000Z","msg":"皇帝隻狗？"},{"pid":"c4ef4b3bd4637da73a4f366a1154533d5ed4fcbb","tid":1908994,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e15b808f15559d743d36c927ba60e69d68fc8c2b","tid":1908994,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34b70e00346e6a126434947cc80979bbe65f45dc","tid":1908994,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislik